lting galaxy pairs observed with HST\nwill provide sufficient priors to improve (optical) SNIa measurements to the\nnext required accuracy in Cosmology.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 May 2015 03:07:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-18"}
